&gt;Droidcon SF 2022&lt;/a&gt;, first conference outside of South Africa after the lockdown years. I was so happy to be part of the speakers for my talk titled &lt;code&gt;Something old, something new - adding Jetpack Compose to a large open source app&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://www.maiatoday.net/p/droidcon-sf-22/dcsf22_maia.jpg"
width="2048"
height="1536"
srcset="https://www.maiatoday.net/p/droidcon-sf-22/dcsf22_maia_hu_aeb2aab0ccf8a600.jpg 480w, https://www.maiatoday.net/p/droidcon-sf-22/dcsf22_maia_hu_377a773778b4ee7c.jpg 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="On stage"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="133"
data-flex-basis="320px"
